tiles.script:
<% $logClass '*' == %>
<% '~.*' 'logClass' STORE %>
IFT
<% $logClass 'Infos' == %>
<% 'info' 'logClass' STORE %>
IFT
<% $logClass 'Warnings' == %>
<% 'warning' 'logClass' STORE %>
IFT
<% $logClass 'Errors' == %>
<% 'error' 'logClass' STORE %>
IFT

{
  'token'  $readToken
  'class'  'logs'
  'labels' { 'logClass' $logClass }
  'end' $dtEnd TOLONG
  'start' $dtStart TOLONG 
} FETCH MERGE { NULL NULL } RELABEL 'logs' STORE

{
  'data' $logs
  'globalParams' {
    'elemsCount' 200000
    'tabular' {
      'fixedWidth' true 
      'sortable' true 
      'filterable' false 
      'onTop' false 
      
    }
  }
}

<% $logClass '*' == %>
<% '~.*' 'logClass' STORE %>
IFT
<% $logClass 'Infos' == %>
<% 'info' 'logClass' STORE %>
IFT
<% $logClass 'Warnings' == %>
<% 'warning' 'logClass' STORE %>
IFT
<% $logClass 'Errors' == %>
<% 'error' 'logClass' STORE %>
IFT

{
  'token'  $readToken
  'class'  'logs'
  'labels' { 'logClass' $logClass }
  'end' $dtEnd TOLONG
  'start' $dtStart TOLONG 
} FETCH MERGE { NULL NULL } RELABEL 'logs' STORE
{ 
  'data'  $logs
  'globalParams' { 
    'bounds' {
     'minDate' $dtStart TOLONG 'maxDate' $dtEnd TOLONG
    } 
    'timeMode' 'date'
    'timeZone' 'AUTO' 
  }
}
